+1. `REPORT.md` with the candidate-by-candidate Tao screening.
+2. `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` with:
+   - goal
+   - what was tested
+   - outcome
+   - one key takeaway
+   - whether Step 2 should proceed or be downgraded
