+## Formula Sheet
+
+- [VERIFIED] The exact far-field pressure pairing carried forward from the copied pressure dissection is
+
+  `I_p^far = -∬ p_far div(v_k φ_k^2 ê)`.
+
+- [VERIFIED] Expanding the divergence gives
